def build_and_test(X_tr, X_te, y_tr, y_te, class_weight = None, threshold = False):   
   
    # Build and fit the model
    if class_weight:
        model = DecisionTreeClassifier(class_weight = class_weight)
    else:
        model = DecisionTreeClassifier()
    model.fit(X_tr, y_tr)
    
    # Test the model
    y_pred = model.predict(X_te)
    print('Precision score %s' % precision_score(y_te, y_predicted, average = None))
    print('Recall score %s' % recall_score(y_te, y_predicted, average = None))
    print('F1-score score %s' % f1_score(y_te, y_predicted, average = None))
    print('Accuracy score %s' % accuracy_score(y_te, y_predicted))
    
    y_score = model.predict_proba(X_te)
   
    # Plot metrics 
    plot_roc(y_te, y_score)
    plt.legend(bbox_to_anchor = (1.03, 1), loc = 'upper left')
    plt.xticks(rotation = 90)
    plt.show()
    
    plot_precision_recall(y_te, y_score)
    plt.legend(bbox_to_anchor = (1.03, 1), loc = 'upper left')
    plt.xticks(rotation = 90)
    plt.show()

    print(classification_report(y_te,y_pred))
